// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3870 — Mass File Rename (ransomhouse)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 40a3d811-756a-5956-9ada-ce404b9754fe

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
